<paragraph blockId="66.[151,1437,525,1092]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">
Remarks.—The genus is here reassigned to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Marshall &amp; Moulds" authorityYear="2018" box="[656,788,525,551]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Malagasiini">Malagasiini</taxonomicName>
based on 
<bibRefCitation author="Boulard, M." box="[907,1114,525,552]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" pagination="44 - 53" refId="ref66883" refString="Boulard, M. (1980 b) Un dispositif protecteur secondaire inedit pour le systeme acoustique chez quatre cigales malgaches (Hom. Cicadoidea). Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France, 85, 44 - 53." type="journal article" year="1980">Boulard’s (1980b)</bibRefCitation>
original description and the genetic analysis of 
<bibRefCitation author="Marshall, D. C. &amp; Moulds, M. S. &amp; Hill, K. B. R. &amp; Price, B. W. &amp; Wade, E. J. &amp; Owen, C. J. &amp; Goemans, G. &amp; Marathe, K. &amp; Sarkar, V. &amp; Cooley, J. R. &amp; Sanborn, A. F. &amp; Kunte, K. &amp; Villet, M. H. &amp; Simon, C." box="[365,625,561,588]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" pagination="1 - 64" refId="ref69587" refString="Marshall, D. C., Moulds, M. S., Hill, K. B. R., Price, B. W., Wade, E. J., Owen, C. J., Goemans, G., Marathe, K., Sarkar, V., Cooley, J. R., Sanborn, A. F., Kunte, K., Villet, M. H. &amp; Simon, C. (2018 b) A molecular phylogeny of the cicadas (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) with a review of tribe and subfamily level classification. Zootaxa, 4424 (1), 1 - 64. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4424.1.1" type="journal article" year="2018">
Marshall 
<emphasis box="[471,520,561,587]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">et al</emphasis>
. (2018b)
</bibRefCitation>
. Although only the habitus of the genus and the ventral sound system are illustrated, the presence of the uncus along with the structural affinities to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1866" box="[990,1091,597,623]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Quintilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[990,1091,597,623]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">Quintilia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Boulard, M." box="[1250,1436,597,624]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" pagination="44 - 53" refId="ref66883" refString="Boulard, M. (1980 b) Un dispositif protecteur secondaire inedit pour le systeme acoustique chez quatre cigales malgaches (Hom. Cicadoidea). Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France, 85, 44 - 53." type="journal article" year="1980">Boulard (1980b)</bibRefCitation>
prevents retaining the current assignment in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1905" box="[641,744,633,659]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Parnisini">Parnisini</taxonomicName>
. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1866" box="[753,854,633,659]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Quintilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[753,854,633,659]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">Quintilia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was transferred to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Marshall &amp; Moulds" authorityYear="2018" box="[1064,1196,633,659]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Malagasiini">Malagasiini</taxonomicName>
with the formation of the tribe as the genetic analyses grouped the genus with the 
<collectingCountry box="[814,949,669,695]" name="Madagascar" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
genera (
<bibRefCitation author="Marshall, D. C. &amp; Moulds, M. S. &amp; Hill, K. B. R. &amp; Price, B. W. &amp; Wade, E. J. &amp; Owen, C. J. &amp; Goemans, G. &amp; Marathe, K. &amp; Sarkar, V. &amp; Cooley, J. R. &amp; Sanborn, A. F. &amp; Kunte, K. &amp; Villet, M. H. &amp; Simon, C." box="[1044,1289,669,696]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" pagination="1 - 64" refId="ref69587" refString="Marshall, D. C., Moulds, M. S., Hill, K. B. R., Price, B. W., Wade, E. J., Owen, C. J., Goemans, G., Marathe, K., Sarkar, V., Cooley, J. R., Sanborn, A. F., Kunte, K., Villet, M. H. &amp; Simon, C. (2018 b) A molecular phylogeny of the cicadas (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) with a review of tribe and subfamily level classification. Zootaxa, 4424 (1), 1 - 64. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4424.1.1" type="journal article" year="2018">
Marshall 
<emphasis box="[1152,1200,669,695]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">et al</emphasis>
. 2018b
</bibRefCitation>
). The habitus image (
<bibRefCitation author="Boulard, M." box="[234,403,705,732]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" pagination="44 - 53" refId="ref66883" refString="Boulard, M. (1980 b) Un dispositif protecteur secondaire inedit pour le systeme acoustique chez quatre cigales malgaches (Hom. Cicadoidea). Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France, 85, 44 - 53." type="journal article" year="1980">Boulard 1980b</bibRefCitation>
) shows the costa and radius &amp; subcostal veins are close together and the uncus appears to be above the long abdominal sternite VIII. In addition, 
<bibRefCitation author="Boulard, M." box="[736,922,741,768]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" pagination="44 - 53" refId="ref66883" refString="Boulard, M. (1980 b) Un dispositif protecteur secondaire inedit pour le systeme acoustique chez quatre cigales malgaches (Hom. Cicadoidea). Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France, 85, 44 - 53." type="journal article" year="1980">Boulard (1980b)</bibRefCitation>
describes the presence of a dorsal beak, elongated pygofer distal shoulders, and an uncus that is similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Distant" authorityYear="1882" box="[838,958,777,803]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Malagasia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[838,958,777,803]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">Malagasia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. These data suggest the genus is a member of the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Marshall &amp; Moulds" authorityYear="2018" box="[223,355,813,839]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Malagasiini">Malagasiini</taxonomicName>
and is reassigned here.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="66.[151,1437,525,1092]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Boulard" authorityYear="1980" box="[199,317,849,875]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadidae" genus="Malgotilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[199,317,849,875]" italics="true" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">Malgotilia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is another monospecific genus represented by a small, stocky cicada with a triangular head and prothorax. The genus is characterized by the subconical head that is much narrower than the mesonotum, forming an approximate triangle with the angled lateral pronotum and prominent anterior postclypeus, the rounded anterior frons margin forming an obtuse angle to the supra-antennal plates, the stocky, cylindroconical male abdomen shorter than the distance between the anterior margin of the postclypeus and posterior cruciform elevation, and an elongated male sternite VIII terminating in a point.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="66.[151,1437,525,1092]" box="[199,1332,1065,1092]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">
Distribution.—The only species of the genus is found in 
<collectingCountry box="[835,970,1065,1091]" name="Madagascar" pageId="66" pageNumber="67">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Duffels, J. P. &amp; van der Laan, P. A." box="[985,1319,1065,1092]" pageId="66" pageNumber="67" refId="ref68709" refString="Duffels, J. P. &amp; van der Laan, P. A. (1985) Catalogue of the Cicadoidea (Homoptera, Auchenorhyncha) 1956 - 1980. Series Entomologica 34. Dr. W. Junk Publishers, Dordrect, 414 pp." type="book" year="1985">Duffels &amp; van der Laan 1985</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
